<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id9024de00-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s2797b–2"><num value="2797b–2">§ 2797b–2.</num><heading> Authority relating to MTCR adherents</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Notwithstanding <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2797b/b">section 2797b(b) of this title</ref>, the President may take the actions under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2797b/a/2">section 2797b(a)(2) of this title</ref> under the circumstances described in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2797c/b/2">section 2797c(b)(2) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id9024de01-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/629">Pub. L. 90–629</ref>, ch. 7, § 73B, as added <ref href="/us/pl/106/113/dB/s1000/a/7/dB/tXI/s1137">Pub. L. 106–113, div. B, § 1000(a)(7) [div. B, title XI, § 1137]</ref>, <date date="1999-11-29">Nov. 29, 1999</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/113/1536">113 Stat. 1536</ref>, 1501A–496).</sourceCredit>
